== 版本 ==
MPEG-H由以下几部分构成：<ref name=MPEGApril2013WorkPlan/><ref name=MPEGHJune2013Website>{{cite news |title=MPEG-H |publisher=Moving Picture Experts Group |url=http://mpeg.chiariglione.org/standards/mpeg-h |accessdate=2013-06-14 |archive-date=2020-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028235352/https://mpeg.chiariglione.org/standards/mpeg-h |dead-url=no }}</ref>
*MPEG-H Part 1：MPEG媒体传输（MMT）<ref name=MMTApril2013DIS/> － 一种适用于不同网络下的媒体流格式。<ref name=MPEGHJune2013Website/><ref name=NHKOpenHouse2013Exhibit18>{{cite news |title=Media Transport Technologies for Next Generation Broadcasting Systems |publisher=[[NHK|NHK]] |url=http://www.nhk.or.jp/strl/open2013/tenji/tenji18/index_e.html |accessdate=2013-06-21 |archive-date=2020-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804061056/http://www.nhk.or.jp/strl/open2013/tenji/tenji18/index_e.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
*MPEG-H Part 2：[[高效率視訊編碼|高效率視訊編碼]]（HEVC／H.265）（和[[ITU-T|ITU-T]] 影片编码专家组联合开发）<ref name=HEVCMay2013FDIS/><ref name=OverviewHEVCIEEE2012>{{cite news |title=Overview of the High Efficiency Video Coding (HEVC) Standard |author=G.J. Sullivan |author2=J.-R. Ohm |author3=W.-J. Han |author4=T. Wiegand |publisher=IEEE Transactions on Circuits and Systems for Video Technology |url=http://iphome.hhi.de/wiegand/assets/pdfs/2012_12_IEEE-HEVC-Overview.pdf |format=PDF |date=2012-05-25 |accessdate=2013-06-14 |archive-date=2020-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200108191736/http://iphome.hhi.de/wiegand/assets/pdfs/2012_12_IEEE-HEVC-Overview.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=HEVCITURecommendationH265>{{cite news |title=H.265 : High efficiency video coding |publisher=ITU |url=http://www.itu.int/rec/T-REC-H.265 |date=2013-06-07 |accessdate=2013-06-14 |archive-date=2021-01-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210101163624/https://www.itu.int/rec/T-REC-H.265 |dead-url=no }}</ref> － 一种影片压缩标准，相比H.264/MPEG-4 AVC 数据压缩率增加了1倍，分辨率支持最高可达8192×4320。<ref name=MPEGHJune2013Website/><ref name=OverviewHEVCIEEE2012/><ref name=HEVCITURecommendationH265/><ref name=PCWorldEricsson>{{cite news |title=New Video Compression Technology Will Cut Bandwidth Use in Half, Says Ericsson |publisher=PCWorld |url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/261252/new_video_compression_technology_will_cut_bandwidth_use_in_half_says_ericsson.html |date=2012-08-22 |accessdate=2013-06-21 |archive-date=2020-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127145755/https://www.pcworld.com/article/261252/new_video_compression_technology_will_cut_bandwidth_use_in_half_says_ericsson.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
*MPEG-H Part 3：3D音频<ref name=MPEGApril2013WorkPlan/> － 一种可以支持多扬声器的3D音频压缩标准。<ref name=MPEGHJune2013Website/>
*MPEG-H Part 5：HEVC一致性测试和基准软件。<ref name=MPEGH5April2013CD/>
*MPEG-H Part 8：HEVC一致性测试。<ref name=MPEGH8May2013CD/>

